1
00:00:42,792 --> 00:00:45,962
LIKE FLOWERS IN SAND

2
00:00:47,005 --> 00:00:48,715
<i>Oh Du-sik.</i>

3
00:00:49,174 --> 00:00:51,968
<i>Lahir pada 23 Ogos 1992.</i>

4
00:00:53,928 --> 00:00:56,347
<i>Dia anak perempuan tunggal Jaguh Oh Jun</i>

5
00:00:56,431 --> 00:00:59,017
<i>yang terkenal pada tahun 80-an dan 90-an.</i>

6
00:00:59,100 --> 00:01:02,228
<i>Du-sik ada keistimewaan sendiri.</i>

7
00:01:03,605 --> 00:01:06,024
- Apa itu?
- Tolong pegang sekejap.

8
00:01:07,108 --> 00:01:08,902
Kenapa mesti saya?

9
00:01:08,985 --> 00:01:13,281
<i>Dia ketua geng budak-budak kampung kami.</i>

10
00:01:13,364 --> 00:01:16,576
<i>Dia terkenal kerana sifatnya</i>
<i>yang lincah dan lasak.</i>

11
00:01:16,659 --> 00:01:19,204
- Mungkin dia dapat tangkap cicak.
- Cicak?

12
00:01:20,330 --> 00:01:22,373
- Awak tangkap cicak?
- Nak tengok.

13
00:01:23,500 --> 00:01:26,419
<i>Tapi yang paling utama, dia sangat berani.</i>

14
00:01:34,886 --> 00:01:37,847
"Mari pergi ke hutan.

15
00:01:38,973 --> 00:01:41,768
Mari mengutip cebisan bintang di hutan."

16
00:01:43,895 --> 00:01:46,731
Penyajak Yoon Dong-ju
sentiasa bermuhasabah diri.

17
00:01:46,815 --> 00:01:47,899
Tolong beri dia.

18
00:01:48,900 --> 00:01:51,528
Beliau malu kerana beliau
lebih aktif bergiat

19
00:01:51,611 --> 00:01:55,240
dalam gerakan kemerdekaan
ketika Korea dijajah oleh Jepun.

20
00:01:56,407 --> 00:01:57,951
Keinginannya untuk merdeka

21
00:01:58,034 --> 00:01:59,327
- dan muhasabah…
- <i>Hei.</i>

22
00:01:59,410 --> 00:02:03,123
<i>Awak nampak hodoh pada waktu siang.</i>

23
00:02:11,464 --> 00:02:14,592
<i>Dan dia panas baran.</i>

24
00:02:14,676 --> 00:02:18,638
<i>Semua budak lelaki di kampung</i>
<i>pernah dibelasah oleh Du-sik.</i>

25
00:02:25,270 --> 00:02:27,647
Sudahlah, Du-sik. Berhenti.

26
00:02:34,612 --> 00:02:35,530
<i>Dan…</i>

27
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:38,741
Hei, Kim Baek-du.

28
00:02:39,242 --> 00:02:42,912
Jangan kalah dengan perempuan.
Buat malu saja.

29
00:02:44,247 --> 00:02:47,208
- Hati-hati. Dia handal.
- Ayuh, Du-sik!

30
00:02:47,292 --> 00:02:48,418
Du-sik!

31
00:02:48,501 --> 00:02:52,505
- Du-sik!
- Du-sik pasti menang!

32
00:02:54,132 --> 00:02:55,383
Ayuh, Du-sik!

33
00:02:57,218 --> 00:02:58,720
Ayuh, Du-sik!

34
00:02:59,596 --> 00:03:02,891
Ayuh, Du-sik!

35
00:03:22,035 --> 00:03:25,997
<i>Dia pemain </i>ssireum<i> terbaik</i>
<i>antara kami semua.</i>

36
00:03:30,460 --> 00:03:35,465
EPISOD 2
ADA SESUATU TENTANG OH DU-SIK

37
00:03:37,425 --> 00:03:38,551
Betul, bukan?

38
00:03:38,635 --> 00:03:39,886
Awak Oh Du-sik.

39
00:03:42,847 --> 00:03:44,432
{\an8}Betulkah awak Du-sik?

40
00:03:44,515 --> 00:03:46,893
{\an8}Du-sik, awak…

41
00:03:46,976 --> 00:03:49,938
{\an8}Hei! Sampai hati awak buat saya begini?

42
00:03:50,021 --> 00:03:52,398
{\an8}Lama saya tunggu khabar daripada awak!

43
00:03:52,482 --> 00:03:55,151
{\an8}Awak sepatutnya tinggalkan nota
sebelum pergi

44
00:03:55,235 --> 00:03:56,402
{\an8}atau hubungi saya!

45
00:03:56,486 --> 00:03:58,613
{\an8}Awak tahu alamat dan nombor saya.

46
00:03:58,696 --> 00:04:01,157
{\an8}Awak boleh hubungi saya kalau awak mahu!

47
00:04:01,241 --> 00:04:03,743
{\an8}Sampai hati awak menghilang begitu saja?

48
00:04:03,826 --> 00:04:06,120
{\an8}Tergamaknya awak.

49
00:04:07,664 --> 00:04:11,042
{\an8}Tapi awak kembali.
Itu lebih penting, bukan?

50
00:04:12,210 --> 00:04:13,419
{\an8}Selamat kembali.

51
00:04:17,507 --> 00:04:19,133
Kenapa, Du-sik?

52
00:04:20,051 --> 00:04:23,179
Kenapa tak ada reaksi langsung?

53
00:04:23,263 --> 00:04:24,973
Awak tak gembira jumpa saya?

54
00:04:25,056 --> 00:04:26,516
Awak tak rindu saya?

55
00:04:27,016 --> 00:04:29,394
- Saya…
- Saya sangat rindu awak.

56
00:04:33,314 --> 00:04:34,899
<i>Du-sik perempuan?</i>

57
00:04:35,566 --> 00:04:36,526
Ya.

58
00:04:37,735 --> 00:04:40,238
Kenapa saya sangka dia lelaki?

59
00:04:40,321 --> 00:04:42,532
Tiada siapa pun cakap Du-sik lelaki.

60
00:04:43,449 --> 00:04:45,368
Betul juga.

61
00:04:45,451 --> 00:04:49,330
Saya sangka dia lelaki
kerana namanya Du-sik.

62
00:04:49,414 --> 00:04:53,710
Ya, nama dia macam lelaki.
Dan dia selalu buat kacau, jadi…

63
00:04:53,793 --> 00:04:54,794
Begitu rupanya.

64
00:04:55,628 --> 00:04:58,381
- Jadi Du-sik perempuan.
- Ya.

65
00:04:58,464 --> 00:05:01,759
Sebab itulah dia asyik
sebut-sebut nama Du-sik hari itu.

66
00:05:01,843 --> 00:05:03,594
- Apa?
- Apa?

67
00:05:03,678 --> 00:05:04,804
Tak ada apa-apa.

68
00:05:06,097 --> 00:05:09,809
Jadi apa cerita Du-sik?

69
00:05:11,269 --> 00:05:12,729
Cakaplah.

70
00:05:12,812 --> 00:05:15,106
Awak tak nak cerita sebab saya orang luar?

71
00:05:15,189 --> 00:05:19,235
Bukan sebab itu.
Saya tak tahu sangat apa yang terjadi.

72
00:05:20,278 --> 00:05:23,114
Pak Cik Tae-baek, Pak Cik Jun
dan Du-sik saja tahu.

73
00:05:25,283 --> 00:05:28,578
Jadi jangan cakap tentang Du-sik
di tempat lain.

74
00:05:29,787 --> 00:05:30,621
Kenapa?

75
00:05:31,622 --> 00:05:33,624
Sebab ia bukan hal yang baik.

76
00:05:36,586 --> 00:05:37,712
Saya bukan dia.

77
00:05:37,795 --> 00:05:39,172
Apa awak cakap, Du-sik?

78
00:05:40,798 --> 00:05:42,592
Saya cakap saya bukan dia.

79
00:05:42,675 --> 00:05:43,593
Apa maksud awak?

80
00:05:43,676 --> 00:05:47,180
Rasanya awak salah orang.
Saya bukan Oh Du-sik.

81
00:05:49,057 --> 00:05:52,143
Apa? Tunggu dulu. Hei.

82
00:05:52,226 --> 00:05:54,937
Awak bukan Oh Du-sik?

83
00:05:55,772 --> 00:05:56,731
Jadi awak siapa?

84
00:06:00,318 --> 00:06:01,444
Maaf.

85
00:06:02,195 --> 00:06:04,405
Cik ini siapa?

86
00:06:04,489 --> 00:06:05,990
Perlukah saya beritahu?

87
00:06:07,325 --> 00:06:08,743
Tolong pergi dari sini.

88
00:06:08,826 --> 00:06:11,204
Awak dah dikira menceroboh.

89
00:06:11,287 --> 00:06:12,121
Apa?

90
00:06:16,667 --> 00:06:17,835
Tapi…

91
00:06:20,296 --> 00:06:21,964
Saya pasti dia Du-sik.

92
00:06:24,258 --> 00:06:25,510
Putih.

93
00:06:26,886 --> 00:06:28,554
Putih?

94
00:06:30,515 --> 00:06:32,391
Putih, mana awak?

95
00:06:41,651 --> 00:06:42,985
Putih.

96
00:06:44,487 --> 00:06:45,696
Putih.

97
00:06:49,492 --> 00:06:51,869
Awak ada di sini? Putih?

98
00:06:53,246 --> 00:06:54,622
Putih!

99
00:06:55,748 --> 00:06:58,000
Ada sesuatu yang mencurigakan, bukan?

100
00:06:58,668 --> 00:07:00,920
Bau apa ini?

101
00:07:01,003 --> 00:07:03,047
Ada najislah.

102
00:07:03,923 --> 00:07:05,550
- Tak guna.
- Jijiknya.

103
00:07:05,633 --> 00:07:09,720
Tentu Putih menyorok di sini.

104
00:07:10,346 --> 00:07:12,265
Saya maksudkan kes di takungan.

105
00:07:12,348 --> 00:07:14,725
Banyak hal yang mencurigakan.

106
00:07:14,809 --> 00:07:16,436
Sudahlah.

107
00:07:16,519 --> 00:07:21,482
Rohnya tentu tak tenang sebab awak.

108
00:07:21,566 --> 00:07:23,484
Kalau rohnya tak tenang,

109
00:07:23,568 --> 00:07:26,696
tentu sebab dia dianiaya,
bukan sebab saya.

110
00:07:26,779 --> 00:07:29,365
Sebab kematiannya tak dipedulikan.

111
00:07:29,449 --> 00:07:31,075
Aduhai.

112
00:07:31,159 --> 00:07:32,994
Awak tak rasa pelikkah?

113
00:07:33,077 --> 00:07:36,247
Kenapa dia mati di kampung
yang tiada kaitan dengan dia?

114
00:07:36,330 --> 00:07:38,916
Dan kenapa dia lemas dalam takungan

115
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:41,461
yang kebanyakan penduduk tak tahu pun?

116
00:07:41,544 --> 00:07:46,132
Hei, ajal dan maut di tangan Tuhan.

117
00:07:46,215 --> 00:07:48,593
Apa yang peliknya?

118
00:07:48,676 --> 00:07:51,637
Jangan merepek lagi dan cepat cari Putih.

119
00:07:51,721 --> 00:07:53,181
Macam mana dengan CCTV?

120
00:07:53,806 --> 00:07:57,518
Pegawai dari Seoul ambil semua
rakaman CCTV di kampung.

121
00:07:57,602 --> 00:08:00,688
Kenapa? Bukan ada apa-apa
yang menarik di sini.

122
00:08:02,607 --> 00:08:03,816
Saya pasti

123
00:08:03,900 --> 00:08:07,403
ada kisah di sebaliknya.
Ini bukan kemalangan.

124
00:08:07,487 --> 00:08:08,529
Kalau bukan pun?

125
00:08:08,613 --> 00:08:11,157
Apa yang awak boleh buat?

126
00:08:11,741 --> 00:08:13,910
- Saya akan siasat.
- Aduhai.

127
00:08:13,993 --> 00:08:16,370
Walaupun rakaman CCTV dah tiada,

128
00:08:16,954 --> 00:08:18,789
saya akan cari jalan lain.

129
00:08:18,873 --> 00:08:21,792
Jangan buat hal.

130
00:08:21,876 --> 00:08:25,546
Saya tak nak buat kerja remeh macam

131
00:08:25,630 --> 00:08:27,048
mencari anjing hilang…

132
00:08:27,131 --> 00:08:30,760
Putih!

133
00:08:31,969 --> 00:08:33,930
Putih!

134
00:08:34,514 --> 00:08:36,766
Putih!

135
00:08:40,686 --> 00:08:41,687
Hei. Kejar!

136
00:08:41,771 --> 00:08:43,689
- Putih!
- Cepat!

137
00:08:44,649 --> 00:08:46,025
Aduhai.

138
00:08:46,817 --> 00:08:49,946
- Dia memang bagus.
- Hei, datang sini balik!

139
00:08:50,905 --> 00:08:52,031
Putih!

140
00:08:53,199 --> 00:08:54,450
Rumah itu?

141
00:08:54,534 --> 00:08:57,036
Bukankah rumah itu dah lama kosong?

142
00:08:57,119 --> 00:08:59,497
- Ya. Tapi saya dengar…
- Putih!

143
00:08:59,580 --> 00:09:01,415
ada penghuni baru malam tadi.

144
00:09:01,499 --> 00:09:02,875
Malam tadi?

145
00:09:02,959 --> 00:09:04,252
- Aduhai.
- Tengoklah.

146
00:09:04,335 --> 00:09:05,545
Apa dia?

147
00:09:05,628 --> 00:09:08,839
Lari, Putih!

148
00:09:10,007 --> 00:09:12,426
- Anjing itu melatih dia.
- Lari!

149
00:09:12,510 --> 00:09:13,844
Awak kejar Putih lagi?

150
00:09:14,387 --> 00:09:15,721
Berhenti!

151
00:09:18,015 --> 00:09:18,891
Hei!

152
00:09:21,185 --> 00:09:22,603
Berhenti!

153
00:09:55,219 --> 00:09:57,555
Jadi dia akan masuk pasukan mana?

154
00:09:58,389 --> 00:10:01,183
Entahlah. Khabarnya dia dapat
banyak tawaran.

155
00:10:01,267 --> 00:10:02,893
Dia akan pilih gaji tinggi.

156
00:10:02,977 --> 00:10:05,855
Tapi tentu En. Hong tak mahu dia pergi.

157
00:10:05,938 --> 00:10:08,149
Taklah.

158
00:10:08,232 --> 00:10:11,027
Tentu dia seronok sekarang.

159
00:10:11,861 --> 00:10:15,990
Dia dah lama nak bubarkan
pasukan <i>ssireum</i> itu.

160
00:10:16,073 --> 00:10:18,993
Dia tak bubarkan selama ini
sebab Lim Dong-seok.

161
00:10:19,577 --> 00:10:22,913
Maknanya pasukan <i>ssireum</i> itu
mungkin akan dibubarkan?

162
00:10:23,873 --> 00:10:26,751
Apa kata awak pergi bincang
dengan En. Hong?

163
00:10:26,834 --> 00:10:28,919
Rasanya tak patut kalau saya suruh

164
00:10:29,003 --> 00:10:31,589
dia tolong pasukan anak saya…

165
00:10:32,298 --> 00:10:33,799
Tapi Baek-du dah bersara.

166
00:10:35,676 --> 00:10:37,720
Apa? Dia sendiri yang cakap.

167
00:10:37,803 --> 00:10:41,849
Dia cakap dia akan bersara
kalau dia tak menang kejohanan kali ini.

168
00:10:41,932 --> 00:10:44,226
Ramai tak setuju dengan keputusan juri.

169
00:10:44,310 --> 00:10:46,812
Boleh kata Baek-du yang menang.

170
00:10:46,896 --> 00:10:49,982
Apa pun, dia kalah. Itu hakikatnya.

171
00:10:50,066 --> 00:10:52,401
- Hei!
- Apa awak cakap?

172
00:10:54,195 --> 00:10:56,572
Apa khabar Baek-du? Dia okey?

173
00:10:56,656 --> 00:10:59,367
Tentu dia sedih.
Dia masih berselera makan?

174
00:10:59,450 --> 00:11:02,662
Tentulah dia kecewa.
Saya pasti dia tak ada selera.

175
00:11:03,663 --> 00:11:06,248
Suruhlah dia datang ke sini.

176
00:11:06,332 --> 00:11:07,625
Saya belanja daging…

177
00:11:07,708 --> 00:11:12,713
Baek-du makan besar selepas perlawanan
dan keluar awal pagi tadi.

178
00:11:16,926 --> 00:11:19,303
Bolehkah rahsiakan identiti begini?

179
00:11:23,808 --> 00:11:25,184
Tak guna.

180
00:11:31,524 --> 00:11:33,275
Kenapa datang pagi-pagi begini?

181
00:11:33,359 --> 00:11:35,903
Hei, Seok-hui. Boleh tak…

182
00:11:36,779 --> 00:11:39,573
Hei, ada bau najislah.

183
00:11:39,657 --> 00:11:41,242
Awak buang air dalam seluar?

184
00:11:42,159 --> 00:11:43,619
Cakaplah awak nak apa.

185
00:11:43,702 --> 00:11:46,580
Saya penat berlari-lari.
Berdiri pun tak larat.

186
00:11:47,164 --> 00:11:48,958
Seok-hui, saya cuma nak tanya…

187
00:11:49,041 --> 00:11:52,253
kalau awak boleh…

188
00:11:52,336 --> 00:11:53,796
- tolong saya…
- Baliklah.

189
00:11:53,879 --> 00:11:56,549
Apa? Saya tak habis cakap lagi.

190
00:11:56,632 --> 00:11:58,592
Cakaplah cepat.

191
00:11:58,676 --> 00:12:02,263
Yang kamu biasa buat di sini…

192
00:12:02,346 --> 00:12:04,598
Tunggu.

193
00:12:05,599 --> 00:12:07,059
Selidik latar belakang.

194
00:12:07,601 --> 00:12:10,104
- Boleh buat tak?
- Selidik latar belakang?

195
00:12:10,604 --> 00:12:11,897
Kenapa tiba-tiba saja?

196
00:12:12,565 --> 00:12:14,191
Saya…

197
00:12:14,275 --> 00:12:16,610
- Awak kena tipu?
- Tak, bukan begitu.

198
00:12:16,694 --> 00:12:19,196
Saya dah agak awak
akan jadi mangsa penipu.

199
00:12:19,280 --> 00:12:21,574
- Bukan sebab itulah.
- Bukan?

200
00:12:22,074 --> 00:12:23,117
Jadi sebab apa?

201
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:25,202
Awak boleh buat atau tidak?

202
00:12:25,286 --> 00:12:28,539
Tak boleh, kami cuma boleh buat
untuk membantu siasatan.

203
00:12:29,415 --> 00:12:32,168
Kenapa? Awak nak selidik
latar belakang siapa?

204
00:12:37,006 --> 00:12:37,882
Perempuan itu?

205
00:12:39,091 --> 00:12:42,011
Awak nak tahu kalau dia Du-sik atau bukan?

206
00:12:42,094 --> 00:12:43,095
Ya.

207
00:12:43,888 --> 00:12:46,056
Perlukah selidik latar belakang?

208
00:12:46,140 --> 00:12:48,517
Tengok saja pun dah tahu.

209
00:12:48,601 --> 00:12:49,518
Yakah?

210
00:12:50,019 --> 00:12:51,395
Jadi apa pendapat awak?

211
00:12:51,896 --> 00:12:54,773
Awak gilakah?
Dia tak seiras Du-sik langsung.

212
00:12:54,857 --> 00:12:56,108
Apa? Itu bukan dia?

213
00:12:56,692 --> 00:12:58,444
Awak dah lupa muka Du-sik?

214
00:12:58,527 --> 00:12:59,862
Mereka seiraslah.

215
00:12:59,945 --> 00:13:02,198
Aduhai, awak dah gila agaknya.

216
00:13:02,281 --> 00:13:06,410
Hei, dia banyak kali belasah saya
semasa kecil sebab cakap dia hodoh.

217
00:13:06,494 --> 00:13:08,329
Kita selalu rindu masa silam,

218
00:13:08,412 --> 00:13:10,789
tapi ini dah tahap mengubah masa silam.

219
00:13:10,873 --> 00:13:13,667
- Jadi itu bukan dia?
- Mestilah bukan.

220
00:13:13,751 --> 00:13:17,338
Cuba awak fikir.

221
00:13:17,421 --> 00:13:18,756
Kalau awak Du-sik…

222
00:13:20,758 --> 00:13:22,343
awak mahukah kembali ke sini?

223
00:13:26,138 --> 00:13:27,723
Awak tahu tak?

224
00:13:28,557 --> 00:13:31,519
Du-sik lebih hodoh pada waktu siang.

225
00:13:34,021 --> 00:13:35,606
Betulkah itu bukan dia?

226
00:13:45,199 --> 00:13:46,116
Pergi.

227
00:13:47,117 --> 00:13:48,536
Tolonglah pergi.

228
00:13:54,291 --> 00:13:55,125
Helo?

229
00:13:56,669 --> 00:13:57,545
Ya.

230
00:13:59,463 --> 00:14:02,466
Belum lagi. Saya baru sampai.

231
00:14:02,967 --> 00:14:06,428
- Sedapnya.
- Sedap betul kimchi ini.

232
00:14:24,655 --> 00:14:26,115
Beom-su, letak di meja kita.

233
00:14:26,198 --> 00:14:27,032
Baik.

